Author: 1sintonia
Text: Thank you! I appreciate the support either way. But yeah it makes it extra difficult to eat healthy. I don’t like a ton of veggies but I do like greens a lot. I’m kinda stress eating between my fasting hours so to not have a salad would mean I’d binge on something silly.

Author: RosieNP
Text: Sad lettuce. Such a good name for it!  I wish I had advice or something, but all I can say is that I'm sorry you have to deal with that. It's hard enough when you have an ED without external food restrictions.
